The paper discusses the use of wireless technologies in the manufacturing industry, which involves the integration of machines, workers, and products. This topic falls under the category of Cybernetics (cs.CY), as it deals with the control and communication of complex systems. The paper also discusses the use of wireless technologies in networking and communication (cs.NI), software engineering (cs.SE), and systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper touches on the issue of security in wireless networks (cs.CR).
